text: F1 2000 may refer to: * The 2000 Formula One season, the 51st FIA Formula One World Championship season * F1 2000 (video game), a video game by EA based on the above F1 season released as part of the EA Sports F1 Series * Formula One 2000 (video game), a video game by Psygnosis, based on the above F1 season * F1 Championship Season 2000, a video game by EA Sports, based on the above F1 season
title: F1 2000 (disambiguation)
